casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Derrick Stacy CHAPPEL, a/k/a Derrick Chapple, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 158021
COA: 336794 Supreme Court of Michigan. April 30, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's December 4, 2018 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that reconsideration of our previous order is warranted. MCR 7.311(G). The motion for reconsideration of the amendment to the arrest warrant pursuant to MCR 7.316 is DENIED.
